Published figures: 
<bibRefCitation author="Emmel" box="[410,633,834,859]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" refString="Emmel, T. C., Minno, M. C. &amp; Drummond, B. A. (1992) Florissant butterflies. A guide to the fossil and present-day species of central Colorado. Stanford University Press, Stanford, x + 118 pp." type="book" year="1992">
